<item>
            <title>[CAMEL-5429] Sending null in body when forcing JMS message type to Object throws an Exception</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CAMEL-5429</link>
                <project id="12311211" key="CAMEL">Camel</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I set &quot;jmsMessageType=Object&quot;, and when I try to send a null in the body, I get an exception. See program and log.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
